<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Andrew </PERSON> <PERSON> Katell </PERSON>, an <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> correspondent in <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION>, has covered the <LOCATION> Nagorno-Karabakh </LOCATION> dispute extensively since it began in February.
